Package: swpc.noaa.gov
Title: NOAA Space Weather Prediction Center Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the NOAA SWPC API. Provides solar wind
    plasma data, interplanetary magnetic field measurements, Kp geomagnetic
    index, and space weather alerts. Includes LLM context injection via
    swpc_context().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
